text: Prospect Avenue may refer to: *Prospect Avenue (Kansas City, Missouri), a street that runs close to U.S. Route 71 *Hollywood Boulevard between 1887 and 1910 *Prospect Avenue (Brooklyn), New York City ==New York City Subway stations== *Prospect Avenue (IRT White Plains Road Line), in the Bronx; serving the trains *Prospect Avenue (BMT Fourth Avenue Line), in Brooklyn; serving the trains
